 of the premium between the perpetual and index price. The platform's Cosmos appchain architecture enables faster settlement compared to traditional DEXs. Funding payments are automatically settled to trader accounts each hour, with rates typically ranging from -0.01% to 0.01% but can spike during high volatility periods."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
